PN,31201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780102991
OL,3,CCanadian 'poison seller' linked to 112
OL,4,Cdeaths of Brits won't face justice in
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,FA Canadian man accused of selling
OL,8,Flethal substances linked to the deaths
OL,9,Fof more than 100 Britons is expected
OL,10,Fto enter a guilty plea in his home
OL,11,Fcountry, but won't face justice in the
OL,12,FUK.
OL,14,FKenneth Law is expected to appear in
OL,15,Fcourt in Ontario, Canada, on Friday,
OL,16,Faccused of aiding suicide after
OL,17,Fallegedly selling 1,200 packages
OL,18,Facross 40 countries, including the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780102991
OL,3,CCanadian 'poison seller' linked to 112
OL,4,Cdeaths of Brits won't face justice in
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,FLaw was also investigated by police in
OL,8,Fthe United States, Italy, Australia
OL,9,Fand New Zealand.
OL,11,FAn investigation by the UK's National
OL,12,FCrime Agency (NCA) into Canada-based
OL,13,Fwebsites selling substances to assist
OL,14,Fwith suicide found that 286
OL,15,Findividuals received packages in the
OL,16,FUK, leading to 112 deaths.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780102991
OL,3,CCanadian 'poison seller' linked to 112
OL,4,Cdeaths of Brits won't face justice in
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,FHowever, despite prosecutors in
OL,8,FOntario bringing Law to court, the NCA
OL,9,Fand CPS have written to the bereaved
OL,10,Ffamilies to tell them they would not
OL,11,Fbe seeking to extradite him to the UK
OL,12,Ffollowing legal proceedings in Canada.
OL,14,FIn the letter sent on Thursday, the
OL,15,FCPS and NCA also said Canadian
OL,16,Fauthorities had confirmed that Law,
OL,17,F60, is expected to plead guilty to
OL,18,Fcharges of aiding suicide there.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780102991
OL,3,CCanadian 'poison seller' linked to 112
OL,4,Cdeaths of Brits won't face justice in
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,FThe letter says: "After careful
OL,8,Fassessment, we agreed that Mr Law
OL,9,Fshould be sentenced for the full
OL,10,Fextent of his offending within a
OL,11,Fsingle sentencing process in Canada.
OL,13,F"This approach is not unusual in cases
OL,14,Finvolving serious offending that
OL,15,Fcrosses international borders.
OL,17,F"We recognise that this may be painful
OL,18,Fto hear, and that some victims and
OL,19,Fbereaved families may have hoped to
OL,20,Fsee a separate prosecution in England
OL,21,Fand Wales.
OL,26,@oD@ROUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780102991
OL,3,CCanadian 'poison seller' linked to 112
OL,4,Cdeaths of Brits won't face justice in
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,F"This difficult decision was reached
OL,8,Fonly after detailed consideration of
OL,9,Fall available options."
OL,11,FFollowing the announcement, the
OL,12,Ffamilies of those from the UK who died
OL,13,Fhave now called for a public inquiry.
OL,15,FThe sister of 21-year-old Aimee
OL,16,FWalton, from Southampton, who died in
OL,17,F2022, said that "doors have been shut"
OL,18,Ffor families seeking justice.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@WO]yD@QOUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780102991
OL,3,CCanadian 'poison seller' linked to 112
OL,4,Cdeaths of Brits won't face justice in
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,F"If our own country will not put
OL,8,Fanyone on trial for these deaths, the
OL,9,Fvery least it can do is hold a proper
OL,10,Finquiry into how they were allowed to
OL,11,Fhappen," Adele Zeynep Walton said.
OL,13,F"The question for our own country is
OL,14,Fsimpler still: who here will examine
OL,15,Fhow the British state let this happen,
OL,16,Fand what it will do so that no other
OL,17,Ffamily goes through it? A foreign
OL,18,Fsentencing hearing cannot answer that.
OL,20,F"Only a statutory public inquiry can."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@HO]uD@AOU|D@AOU|D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780102991
OL,3,CCanadian 'poison seller' linked to 112
OL,4,Cdeaths of Brits won't face justice in
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,FDavid Parfett, the father of
OL,8,Fphilosophy student Thomas Parfett, who
OL,9,Fdied aged 22 after taking his own life
OL,10,Fin Sunbury-on-Thames, Surrey, said: "I
OL,11,Fam angry, but I am not surprised.
OL,13,F"For months, we have been told that
OL,14,Fthe system is working and that
OL,15,Fexisting measures are enough. They are
OL,16,Fnot.
OL,26,@rD@eOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780102991
OL,3,CCanadian 'poison seller' linked to 112
OL,4,Cdeaths of Brits won't face justice in
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,F"If our own country will not put
OL,8,Fanyone on trial for these deaths, the
OL,9,Fvery least it can do is hold a proper
OL,10,Finquiry into how they were allowed to
OL,11,Fhappen."
OL,13,FAndy Burrows, chief executive of Molly
OL,14,FRose Foundation, said: "Bereaved
OL,15,Ffamilies have been campaigning
OL,16,Ftirelessly to hold Kenneth Law to
OL,17,Faccount in the UK and to be told he
OL,18,Fwill not be prosecuted here on the eve
OL,19,Fof his court case in Canada is a
OL,20,Fbitter blow.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@HO]vD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780102991
OL,3,CCanadian 'poison seller' linked to 112
OL,4,Cdeaths of Brits won't face justice in
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,F"Families up and down the country have
OL,8,Fbeen impacted by Law's crimes and
OL,9,Fshould have the right to full justice
OL,10,Fin the UK.
OL,12,F"As long as the pro-suicide forum
OL,13,Fremains online, and while this
OL,14,Fsubstance is available in the UK and
OL,15,Facross borders, more vulnerable people
OL,16,Fare at risk."
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@MO]
