PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780102991
OL,3,CCanadian 'poison seller' linked to 112
OL,4,Cdeaths of Brits won't face justice in
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,FIn its letter, the CPS and NCA also
OL,8,Fsaid that it had been established that
OL,9,FLaw sent 330 products to the UK in
OL,10,Ftotal.
OL,12,FA joint statement by Joanne Jakymec,
OL,13,Fchief crown prosecutor for the CPS,
OL,14,Fand NCA deputy director Craig Turner
OL,15,Fsaid the organisations would be
OL,16,Favailable to support victims and their
OL,17,Ffamilies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780102991
OL,3,CCanadian 'poison seller' linked to 112
OL,4,Cdeaths of Brits won't face justice in
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,F"No outcome in any court can remove
OL,8,Fthe pain victims and their families
OL,9,Fhave suffered. Victims have remained
OL,10,Four priority when making decisions to
OL,11,Fdeliver justice," the statement said.
OL,13,F"The National Crime Agency and Crown
OL,14,FProsecution Service have worked
OL,15,Fclosely with the 45 UK police forces,
OL,16,Fas well as international law
OL,17,Fenforcement, throughout the three-year
OL,18,Finvestigation.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@QO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
